# Bug Museum — ignore build artifacts. Students build these themselves.
# Tracked on purpose: source (*.c/*.h), notes (*.md), and the curated study
# artifacts (asm_*.txt, dec_*.c). Everything compiled is ignored below.

# Variant runnable executables (root build.ps1 -Exe) -> <variant>/bin/<arch>/<config>/
**/bin/

# Capstone build output (each capstone build.ps1) -> capstone/build/<arch>/<config>/
**/build/

# Withheld capstone answer keys + trigger harnesses — must never ship.
# (Each capstone also has its own .gitignore for this; repeated here as a backstop.)
**/_solution/

# Compiled outputs anywhere (belt-and-suspenders for in-place builds)
*.obj
*.exe
*.dll
*.lib
*.exp
*.ilk
*.pdb

# Editor / OS noise
.vs/
*.user
Thumbs.db
